These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, superhero, epic, martial-arts
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, bus, jet-ski, snowmobile
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
2. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
3. the person driving the bus is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
5. the person driving the snowmobile is between the person driving the bus and the person driving the jet-ski##2
6. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | animation     | epic | superhero |
| Transport     | train     | jet-ski | snowmobile  | bus      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, ambient, house, indie
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, roller, motorbike, tram
1. the fan of ambient is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
2. the person driving the tram is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fan of indie is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
4. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
5. the fan of house is on the far right##1
6. the person driving the train is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | r&b | ambient    | indie     | house  |
| Transport     | train    | motorbike | roller | tram |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, hip-hop, salsa, indie
4 different pets are kept: dog, hamster, guinea-pig, pony
1. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the fan of indie##1
4. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the fan of salsa##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop   | salsa   | electronic  | indie |
| Pet           | hamster | pony | guinea-pig | dog  |

