.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, puzzles, gardening, writing
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, turkish, american, russian
1. the russian is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the person who's hobby is writing is between the person who's hobby is camping and the american##2
3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
4. the american is on the left or right of the russian##3
5. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
6. the thai is on the right of the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | puzzles | camping | writing | gardening  |
| Nationality   | turkish  | thai   | russian  | american |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, almond-milk, cola, juice
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, photography, rock-climbing, skydiving
1. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | tea    | almond-milk   | cola | juice    |
| Hobby      | photography | fishing | rock-climbing       | skydiving |

