3. the person driving the helicopter is between the person driving the airplane and the person drinking 7up##2
4. the person driving the bike is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | 7up | mirinda | almond-milk | water |
| Transport   | jet-ski | helicopter  | airplane    | bike  |

