.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, sudoku, cooking, woodworking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, comedy, crime, fantasy
1. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person watching comedy movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
5. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
6. the person watching comedy movies is on the left or right of the person watching crime movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Hobby         | woodworking | cooking | chess | sudoku   |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | crime | drama      | fantasy |

