2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is rowing is the owner of the turtle##1
4. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
5. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left or far right##3
6. the owner of the frog is between the person who's sport is handball and the person who's sport is soccer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Pet     | rabbit | frog   | hedgehog      | turtle      |
| Sport   | handball     | swimming | soccer | rowing |

