2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person driving the car##1
3. the person driving the boat is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
5. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
6. the person driving the subway is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby       | skydiving | gardening | fishing    | video-games      |
| Transport   | subway       | boat       | car | bus |

