.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, sprite, coffee, 7up
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, soccer, skiing, ice-hockey
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
3. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
4. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
6. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
7. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | sprite     | tea     | coffee          | 7up |
| Sport      | climbing | soccer | ice-hockey | skiing  |

 